<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- يَتَضَرَّرْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- أَوْ يَنْسَ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- أَوْ يَخْشَ فَوْتَ حَاضِرَةٍ، أَوِ اخْتِيَارِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> الثَّالِثُ: سَتْرُ العَوْرَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيَجِبُ حَتَّى خَارِجَهَا، وَفِي خَلْوَةٍ وَظُلْمَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- بِمَا لَا يَصِفُ البَشَرَةَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَعَوْرَةُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> رَجُلٍ، وَحُرَّةٍ مُرَاهِقَةٍ، وأَمَةٍ مُطْلَقاً <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: مَا بَيْنَ سُرَّةٍ وَرُكْبَةٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَابْنِ سَبْعٍ إِلَى عَشْرٍ: الفَرْجَانِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَكُلُّ الحُرَّةِ عَوْرَةٌ إِلَّا وَجْهَهَا فِي الصَّلَاةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنِ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- انْكَشَفَ بَعْضُ عَوْرَتِهِ وَفَحُشَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- أَوْ صَلَّى فِي نَجِسٍ، أَوْ غَصْبٍ،<span class="c5"> ثَوْباً أَوْ بُقْعَةً:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أَعَادَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) سقطت من (أ) و (ج).<br>(٢) قوله: (مطلقاً) سقطت من (ب).</p> </div>